# BT — Behavior Tree Sample Nodes

> This module is intentionally excluded from the PigeonLib build. Its CMakeLists.txt is
> prefixed with `_` so CMake never processes it. It is not linked into any target and has
> no dependency on any other engine module.

## Purpose
Reference sample nodes built on BehaviorTree.CPP v3 demonstrating the three node execution
styles: synchronous (`SyncActionNode`), asynchronous (`AsyncActionNode`), and stateful
(`StatefulActionNode`). Intended as a starting point if BehaviorTree.CPP is integrated into
the engine in the future.

## File Location
`Code/PigeonLib/BT/sample_nodes/`
